SQL_STMT_U.val:
Select t.tr_volgnummer, b.be_belastingverdrag , b.be_oms_1, c.cl_naam1, substr(t.tr_optietype,1,3), t.tr_fiscaal_land, t.tr_vruchtrelatie , t.tr_boekdatum from :1 t, :2 b, :3 c, :4 v Where ((t.tr_boekdatum >= ~5 AND t.tr_boekdatum <=~6) AND t.tr_indicatie = 'UITK' AND (t.tr_fiscaal_land >= ~7 AND t.tr_fiscaal_land <=~8) AND (t.tr_vruchtrelatie >= ~9 AND t.tr_vruchtrelatie <= ~10 AND t.tr_rel1 <> t.tr_vruchtrelatie) AND (t.tr_mut_gemaakt <> 'S' AND t.tr_mut_gemaakt <> 's') AND ((b.be_symbool = t.tr_symbool AND b.be_optietype = ' ' AND b.be_expiratiedatum = '00000000' AND b.be_exerciseprijs = 0) AND b.be_qi_rapportage = 1) ) AND ( c.cl_nummer = t.tr_vruchtrelatie AND ((c.cl_adviseur >= NVL(~11,' ') AND c.cl_adviseur <= NVL(~12,' ')) AND (c.cl_relatie_type >= ~13 AND c.cl_relatie_type <= ~14) AND (c.cl_clientgroep >= NVL(~15,' ') AND c.cl_clientgroep <= NVL(~16,' ')) AND (c.cl_afdelingadviseur >= ~17 AND c.cl_afdelingadviseur <= ~18)) ) AND (v.cgv_adviseur(+) = NVL(~19,' ') AND v.cgv_clientgroep(+) = c.cl_clientgroep )AND (v.cgv_clientgroep is not null AND ~20 = 3 OR ~20<>3)
UNION ALL
Select t.tr_volgnummer, b.be_belastingverdrag, b.be_oms_1, c.cl_naam1,substr(t.tr_optietype,1,3), t.tr_fiscaal_land, t.tr_rel1 , t.tr_boekdatum from :1 t, :2 b, :3 c, :4 v Where ((t.tr_boekdatum>= ~5 AND t.tr_boekdatum<=~6) AND t.tr_indicatie = 'UITK' AND (t.tr_fiscaal_land >= ~7 AND t.tr_fiscaal_land <=~8) AND (t.tr_rel1 >= ~9 AND t.tr_rel1 <= ~10 AND (t.tr_vruchtrelatie=0 OR t.tr_rel1 = t.tr_vruchtrelatie)) AND (t.tr_mut_gemaakt <> 'S' AND t.tr_mut_gemaakt <> 's') AND
((b.be_symbool = t.tr_symbool AND b.be_optietype = ' ' AND b.be_expiratiedatum = '00000000' AND b.be_exerciseprijs = 0) AND b.be_qi_rapportage = 1) ) AND ( c.cl_nummer = t.tr_rel1 AND ((c.cl_adviseur >= NVL(~11,' ') AND c.cl_adviseur <= NVL(~12,' ')) AND (c.cl_relatie_type >= ~13 AND c.cl_relatie_type <= ~14) AND (c.cl_clientgroep >= NVL(~15,' ') AND c.cl_clientgroep <= NVL(~16,' ')) AND (c.cl_afdelingadviseur >= ~17 AND c.cl_afdelingadviseur <= ~18)) ) AND (v.cgv_adviseur(+) = NVL(~19,' ') AND v.cgv_clientgroep(+) = c.cl_clientgroep ) AND (v.cgv_clientgroep is not null AND ~20 = 3 OR ~20<>3)
ORDER BY 5 DESC, 6, 2, 7, 8
